skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: internet agent
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill gets top Internet service providers at your zip code (5 digit). After telling the information about available service providers and their offers it will redirect you to a sales representative to place your order.

Possible phrases to say: 
1. Alexa, tell internet agent to find offers
2. Alexa, ask internet agent to find offers
3. best internet plans at 62999
4. best internet offers at 62999 [replace 62999 with your zip code. Where zip code should be exactly 5 digits long.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
